<item>
            <title>[LU-7300] ptlrpc_request_free() after failed ptlrpc_request_pack() leaves an import referenced</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7300</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;many functions (like osc_setattr()) call ptlrpc_request_free() after failed ptlrpc_request_pack() to release the request. this seem to leave the import referenced and then lead to umount getting stuck.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
